Hey! Hey!

124
00:14:01,560 --> 00:14:02,870
What is it?

125
00:14:03,230 --> 00:14:06,660
You don't need to shout so loud;
I can hear you just fine.

126
00:14:08,260 --> 00:14:10,580
Did you find something good?

127
00:14:11,160 --> 00:14:14,840
Yeah! That's my...

128
00:14:15,500 --> 00:14:19,850
...super flashy
Buggy Pirates pirate ship!

129
00:14:22,790 --> 00:14:25,430
