133
00:14:34,220 --> 00:14:36,610
Red?! Red, you say?!

134
00:14:36,610 --> 00:14:40,820
You're saying I have a big, red nose?!

135
00:14:40,820 --> 00:14:42,400
What? My grave?!

136
00:14:45,140 --> 00:14:46,320
Took you long enough.

137
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:51,250
But who did this?! This is morbid!

138
00:14:52,280 --> 00:14:55,780
Not to mention this is
an old wanted poster...

139
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:59,250
Oh? There's someone
on the ground there...

140
00:15:00,290 --> 00:15:01,540
Wha?!

141
00:15:01,970 --> 00:15:06,050
Mohji! Cabaji!
What happened to you guys?!

142
00:15:06,570 --> 00:15:10,010
C-Captain Buggy...

143
00:15:10,550 --> 00:15:13,970
I-It's so good to see you...

144
00:15:15,190 --> 00:15:17,890
I'm so glad you're all right!

145
00:15:17,890 --> 00:15:20,330
I thought we'd never see you again!

146
00:15:20,330 --> 00:15:22,940
I'm so happy, too!

147
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:28,530
But what on earth happened here?

148
00:15:29,640 --> 00:15:31,220
