149
00:15:31,710 --> 00:15:35,820
Eh? We suddenly got
punched out of the blue, so...

150
00:15:36,580 --> 00:15:40,250
Embarrassingly enough,
we can't remember a thing...

151
00:15:41,230 --> 00:15:45,030
The Bear Claw Tribe did this.

152
00:15:46,750 --> 00:15:47,970
Bear Claw Tribe?!

153
00:15:48,260 --> 00:15:51,790
Yeah. If you're going to
save them, you'd better hurry.

154
00:15:53,900 --> 00:15:57,010
Bear Claw tribesmen are famous
for being food connoisseurs.

155
00:16:10,510 --> 00:16:14,010
The captain says that lions taste bad!

156
00:16:14,010 --> 00:16:15,800
We taste bad, too!

157
00:16:15,800 --> 00:16:17,590
I won't be very tasty at all!

158
00:16:17,590 --> 00:16:19,170
This guy tastes way better than me!

159
00:16:19,170 --> 00:16:22,120
Lies! Lies! He tastes much better!

160
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:25,220
I'm too boney! I got nothing to eat!

161
00:16:27,830 --> 00:16:29,120
Don't worry!

162
00:16:29,120 --> 00:16:31,830
We're the Bear Claw Tribe!
We're iron chefs!

163
00:16:32,220 --> 00:16:34,640
Some wine and spices
will take your smell away!

164
00:16:39,420 --> 00:16:41,430
What do we do with this food?

165
00:16:41,430 --> 00:16:42,910
What are they?

166
00:16:42,910 --> 00:16:45,110
I've never seen such
strange ingredients before.

167
00:16:45,520 --> 00:16:46,960
Do we boil it with them?

168
00:16:47,750 --> 00:16:49,910
I just hope it doesn't
give me stomach trouble...

169
00:16:49,910 --> 00:16:51,360
Chop-Chop-Chop...

170
00:16:55,890 --> 00:16:57,870
...Chop-Chop-Chop-Chop...

171
00:17:29,560 --> 00:17:31,070
Is that...?!

172
00:17:34,700 --> 00:17:41,150
Chop-Chop-Chop-Chop
Chop-Chop-Chop...

173
00:17:41,150 --> 00:17:43,620
Flashily reassemble!

174
00:18:12,200 --> 00:18:14,930
I'm back!

175
00:18:16,110 --> 00:18:19,990
--Captain Buggy!
--What?!

176
00:18:22,040 --> 00:18:24,780
Sorry I took so long, men!

177
00:18:26,290 --> 00:18:29,640
Liven things up with
a super flashy Buggy Ball!

178
00:18:39,500 --> 00:18:40,780
Richie!

179
00:18:49,570 --> 00:18:53,170
Acrobat Technique:
Murder at the Steam Bath!

180
00:18:53,580 --> 00:18:56,440
Let the beast-taming show begin!

181
00:19:03,920 --> 00:19:08,250
