everything you did to my men!

183
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:17,700
Here I flashily come!

184
00:19:19,400 --> 00:19:22,240
Chop-Chop Kick!

185
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:29,560
Chop-Chop Punch!

186
00:19:30,310 --> 00:19:32,060
Die flashily!

187
00:19:33,320 --> 00:19:36,820
Chop-Chop Rice Cracker!

188
00:19:38,350 --> 00:19:40,330
Chop-Chop Festival!

189
00:19:42,070 --> 00:19:44,080
Chop-Chop Punch!

190
00:19:44,560 --> 00:19:47,040
Chop-Chop Carnival!

191
00:19:48,020 --> 00:19:49,700
H-He's doing this all for us!

192
00:19:49,700 --> 00:19:51,040
That's our captain!

193
00:19:56,140 --> 00:19:58,610
Captain Buggy!

194
00:20:02,840 --> 00:20:04,850
I'm so glad you're all right!

195
00:20:05,730 --> 00:20:09,810
I've greatly pained you all,
my adorable underlings!

196
00:20:10,180 --> 00:20:13,770
Our pain is nothing at all!

197
00:20:18,960 --> 00:20:20,730
Who're you calling a weird creature?!

198
00:20:23,230 --> 00:20:30,080
All the hardships you had were
because of that damn Straw Hat!

199
00:20:34,150 --> 00:20:37,810
