pretty young woman be?

200
00:20:38,170 --> 00:20:40,300
Don't forget "really cute"!

201
00:20:40,450 --> 00:20:44,150
Y-Yes. I had been
wondering about that myself...

202
00:20:45,440 --> 00:20:48,820
This nice woman saved
my life! Her name is...

203
00:20:49,890 --> 00:20:50,880
U-Uhh...

204
00:20:52,130 --> 00:20:56,560
Umm, I'm sorry.
What was your name again?

205
00:20:59,440 --> 00:21:03,030
Everyone! The Buggy
Pirates are back in action!

206
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:09,110
Captain! What is our first goal now?!

207
00:21:09,440 --> 00:21:13,260
The head of Monkey D. Luffy!

208
00:21:41,120 --> 00:21:43,130
Hey. I think I see an island.

209
00:21:43,450 --> 00:21:45,250
Eh? Really?!

210
00:21:46,690 --> 00:21:48,240
What island is that?!

211
00:21:48,700 --> 00:21:51,180
I just told you the other day!

212
00:21:51,180 --> 00:21:52,030
Huh?

213
00:21:52,280 --> 00:21:54,960
So that's the island where Loguetown is!

214
00:21:57,030 --> 00:21:58,990
