the beginning and end...

224
00:23:10,990 --> 00:23:15,830
My overflowing feelings don't connect

225
00:23:15,990 --> 00:23:20,670
as I firmly squeeze your hand back

226
00:23:20,900 --> 00:23:25,590
I'll set off by myself,

227
00:23:25,830 --> 00:23:30,550
so keep watching me intently
as I go into the distance

228
00:23:35,680 --> 00:23:40,270
I was thinking about it
a bit since this morning

229
00:23:40,680 --> 00:23:45,370
Why is it so hot?

230
00:23:45,370 --> 00:23:55,370
Starting from some point, I haven't
been able to get away from that

231
00:23:56,670 --> 00:24:01,670
I want to catch those
feelings that rushed off,

232
00:24:01,670 --> 00:24:06,510
and I'm already about
to overtake myself, even

233
00:24:06,510 --> 00:24:11,260
I want to embrace my
dreams that have jumped out

234
00:24:11,460 --> 00:24:16,610
With you, I can run there

235
00:24:25,450 --> 00:24:27,710
So this is the city where Gold Roger,
King of the Pirates, died!

236
00:24:27,710 --> 00:24:30,310
This place is filled with great
ingredients and beautiful girls!

237
00:24:30,310 --> 00:24:31,810
Think they got any bargain sales?!

238
00:24:31,810 --> 00:24:33,050
What are you, a housewife?

239
00:24:33,050 --> 00:24:35,040
Climbing the execution platform
and seeing the scenery comes first!

240
00:24:35,040 --> 00:24:36,640
I want some swords, but...

241
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:38,030
Do you have money?

242
00:24:38,030 --> 00:24:40,350
I can lend you some at 300% interest!

243
00:24:40,350 --> 00:24:41,760
On the next episode of One Piece!

244
00:24:41,760 --> 00:24:44,880
"The Town of the Beginning and End;
